snippet.title: Sentinel Agency Annoucement Trailer
snippet.description:
Annoucement Trailer of the new SINGLEPLAYER STORY-DRIVEN SURVIVAL SHOOTER called Sentinel Agency. 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2951380/Sentinel_Agency/
Steam Release on 12/26/2024! 

As a special investigator from the Sentinel Agency you need to solve a murder spree on the dinosaur theme park Giant Valley. Shoot, sneak, uncover secrets and survive!

Steam Release on 12/26/2024! 

#SentinelAgency #gaming #dinosaur
